    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个登出流程的时序图。用户点击退出后，Client要把请求发到AuthService，不是直接找Server。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "AuthService",
        "POST /api/auth/logout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，这个POST /api/auth/logout是从Client发到AuthService的箭头，对吧？那Server这个参与者还需要画进来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "AuthService",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Server要保留，虽然登出逻辑不走Server，但整个系统架构里Server是核心参与者，放在图里上下文更完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我已经加上了Client、Server、AuthService三个参与者。接下来画Client到AuthService的实线箭头，标注POST /api/auth/logout。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "AuthService",
        "POST /api/auth/logout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "AuthService收到请求后，要先check session exists，确认用户真的有登录态，然后再destroy session。这两步都是AuthService自己内部的逻辑，画成自循环箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "check session exists",
        "destroy session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加AuthService的两个自循环：先check session exists，后destroy session。最后返回给Client的响应怎么画？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "check session exists",
        "destroy session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "返回用虚线箭头，200 OK，消息体里写\"Logged out\"，表示登出成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "Client",
        "200 OK",
