      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成。AuthService用虚线返回Client，标注200 OK (\"Logged out\")。整个登出流程：Client请求AuthService，内部校验并销毁session，最后返回成功状态。",
